UPSTREAM DATA SOURCES (cited, not re-licensed by us):
- Sentinel-2 imagery: Copernicus open data (Copernicus Sentinel data 2016-2026).
- Hansen Global Forest Change v1.12: UMD GLAD / Global Forest Watch, public domain.
  Citation: Hansen, M. C., et al. (2013). Science 342(6160), 850-853. DOI:10.1126/science.1244693.
- ESA WorldCover v200: ESA Copernicus, CC-BY-4.0.
  Citation: Zanaga, D., et al. (2021). DOI:10.1038/s41597-021-01044-0.
- Dynamic World v1: Google AI + WRI + NGS, CC-BY-4.0.
- Meta Canopy Height v2: Meta AI / Land & Carbon Lab, CC-BY-4.0.
- GEDI L2A: NASA public domain.
- AlphaEarth Foundations Satellite Embedding V1: Google + DeepMind, CC-BY-4.0.
- OSM LGU polygons: OpenStreetMap contributors, ODbL.
- PSA administrative boundaries: Philippine Statistics Authority public release.
